rioting during Sunday's Land Day mass demonstrations.
</P>
<P>
The order to deploy tanks near the entrances to Palestinian
cities was given by Defense Minister Yitzhak Mordechai after
holding urgent consultations Wednesday night with senior security
officials on the current situation.
</P>
