Association of Southeast Asian Nations (ASEAN), and that Singapore
supported Australia's entry into the grouping, which now comprises
Indonesia, Malaysia, Singapore, the Philippines, Thailand, Brunei,
and Vietnam.
</P>
<P>
Howard is scheduled to visit China from March 28--April 2 after
his visit here.  
