<HEADLINE> Indian Prime Minister Gowda Returns from Moscow </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NEW DELHI, March 27 (Xinhua) -- Indian Prime Minister Deve
Gowda returned here today after concluding his three-day official
visit to Moscow.
</P>
