<HEADLINE> Makinen Wins Portuguese Rally </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LISBON, March 26 (Xinhua) -- Finland's Tommi Makinen, in a
Mitsubishi, took his first victory of the season by taking the
Portuguese Rally in Figueira Da Foz on Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
