Three Ford Escorts finished behind Makinen and Loix. German
Armin Schwarz came third, 6 minutes 33 seconds off the pace,
Belgian Gregoire de Mevius took fourth 12 minutes 28 seconds
behind, and Monte Carlo's Jean-Pierre Richelmi finished fifth with
a deficit of 17 minutes 16 seconds. 
